{"tid":578920,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]香港大事問答卡開箱文","createTime":"2018-03-03T06:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T07:36:11.000Z","uid":59984,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6818422f73eee7751f1f93e2058a6a352dd31f","tid":578920,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早前係蘋果見到年宵有香港歷史遊戲卡賣<br />\n<br />\n【年宵有乜玩】承傳香港歷史記憶 八十後設計排時序卡game - <br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_571502_0&amp;i=20180212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_571502_0%26i%3D20180212&d=%2Fj%2FDjIROJYT7MDUWTicArW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7e4347f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fmagazine%2Fr.php%3Fa%3D2_571502_0%26i%3D20180212&h=585c9cc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/magazine/r.php?a=2_571502_0&amp;i=20180212</a><br />\n<br />\n睇落都好似幾正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住計劃落去買喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係年宵果幾日我無一日得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為錯過咗就無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但早兩日上網見到原來宜家仲有得郵購賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那那聲狗衝過錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日收到掛號信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開箱喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/134512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F134512_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af390846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n偷睇吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/135239_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F135239_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dc28d2b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攞個盒出嚟睇過<br />\n正面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/135436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F135436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4dbc8744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/135459_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F135459_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e546f40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除套開盒影兩野先<br />\n有兩疊卡&amp;遊戲說明紙一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/135528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F135528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9b0c0058&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/140921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F140921_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=92d960cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭約fd玩吓先<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺<br />\n=====================<br />\n淨開箱計<br />\n收到掛號果下係開心嘅<br />\n因為發貨好快<br />\n由過數去到實物到手<br />\n都係兩三日內嘅事<br />\n仲要係掛號<br />\n真心覺得貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但之後見到個盒<br />\n個感覺係有落差<br />\n因為個盒個紙質俾我心目中預期有落差<br />\n因為個盒唔算硬但唔算大事<br />\n個遊戲卡內容先係重點吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為未玩<br />\n所以分享唔到遊戲體驗<br />\n但係香港歷史無價<br />\n買嚟當留俾下一代<br />\n做個歷史小記錄都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n要大聲講一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> Hong Kong is not China</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/140857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F140857_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=19666d39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05c2489f1ffdbed3a7bd4e6fabce76770fad5266","tid":578920,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"9e78c9720f7fc340c9a07e4c118d8150f8cec73f","tid":578920,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c2489f1ffdbed3a7bd4e6fabce76770fad5266","tid":578920,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係打手我就再詳細啲再寫多啲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}